<div class= "destinations">
<h1>Destinations</h1>
<p>The British Virgin Islands are considered the best sailing and boating destination of the Caribbean.  While cruising the crystal clear waters, enjoy the white sandy beaches, great selection of laid-back bars, and restaurants. Travel windward through the British Virgin Islands and catch the trade winds as they carry you to nearby destinations.  The British Virgin Islands has more than 60 islands for anchorage and are contained within an 80 nautical kilometre radius.</p>


<div class= "destinations-content">

   
<!-- Virgin Gorda -->
    <div class= "virgingorda content">
      <div class="islands"><strong><%= link_to "Virgin Gorda", Destination.find_by(name: "Virgin Gorda") %></strong></div>
        <%= image_tag "virgingorda.png", class:"pictures" %>
        <br>
        <dialog id="vgmodal">  
        <h3>Virgin Gorda</h3>  
        <p>Sail to Virgin Gorda to enjoy the quiet coves, safe anchorages, and yacht clubs.  While in Virgin Gorda, see the Baths known for it’s unique natural land formation in the BVI. The Baths consist of thousands of smooth boulders, strewn along the beach on southern end Virgin Gorda. Enjoy a drink at the Top of the Baths, with one of their unique cocktails. Nearby is Virgin Gorda Yacht Harbour, with a full service marina, shops and restaurants. Bitter End Yacht Club, Saba Rock and Leverick Bay all offer good restaurants and transient dockage.</p>  
        <button id="vgexit" class="btn btn-default">Exit</button>  
        </dialog>  
        <button id="vgshow" class="btn btn-default">Show More</button>

        <script type="text/javascript">
          (function() {  
              var dialog = document.getElementById('vgmodal');  
              document.getElementById('vgshow').onclick = function() {  
                  dialog.show();  
              };  
              document.getElementById('vgexit').onclick = function() {  
                  dialog.close();  
              };  
          })();
          </script>
      </div>


<!-- Tortola -->
