        <br>
        <dialog id="tmodal">  
        <h3>Tortola</h3>  
        <p>Tortola is the largest and most populated of the British Virgin Islands.  Tortola has several popular anchorages including Cane Garden Bay, Soper’s Hole, Road Harbour and Marina Cay at Trellis Bay.  The capital of Tortola, Road Town is the starting point for many yacht charters.</p>
        <button id="texit" class="btn btn-default">Exit</button>  
        </dialog>  
        <button id="tshow" class="btn btn-default">Show More</button>
     
        <script type="text/javascript">
