        <br>
        <dialog id="jvdmodal">  
        <h3>Jost Van Dyke</h3>  
        <p>Jost Van Dyke is only accessible by boat, which is an easy and beautiful sail from Tortola.  This island is known for the sandy white beach and the infamous Soggy Dollar Bar named for the soaked dollars handed over by sailors who swam ashore for their well-known libation the Painkiller. </p>
