        <p>Anegada or the "drowned island' is located remotely north.  A sail to this island wouldn’t be complete without enjoying the locally caught lobster.  Cow Wreck Beach Bar and Restaurant, Anegada Reef Hotel Neptune’s Treasure offer fresh caught lobster culinary delights.</p>
